    "Custom.DeveloperNotes": "<div><span><b>Analysis</b>:<br></span> </div><div>PDF converter is positioning images on Y=0, it is better to calculate image height and positioning accordingly.<br> </div><div><br> </div><div><b>Solution</b>:<br> </div><div>Updated PDF DLL code to better positioning images. <br> </div><div><br> </div><div><b>Testing Actually Done:</b><br> </div><div>Created PL images small and normal sizes and then rendered on TOP PL: </div><div><img src=\"https://dev.azure.com/hexagonPPMCOL/ad8b5582-3a1b-45b4-b53f-df3e968b9505/_apis/wit/attachments/f31fecd7-932d-4173-a67c-ba08118d73ea?fileName=image.png\" alt=Image><br> </div><div>Examples: </div><div><img src=\"https://dev.azure.com/hexagonPPMCOL/ad8b5582-3a1b-45b4-b53f-df3e968b9505/_apis/wit/attachments/c26217c6-3c9a-463c-a78f-b362022f92c6?fileName=image.png\" alt=Image style=\"width:328px;\" width=328 height=418><img src=\"https://dev.azure.com/hexagonPPMCOL/ad8b5582-3a1b-45b4-b53f-df3e968b9505/_apis/wit/attachments/8d39a623-9a46-404e-94c5-98cb774545f7?fileName=image.png\" alt=Image style=\"width:293px;\" width=293 height=411><img src=\"https://dev.azure.com/hexagonPPMCOL/ad8b5582-3a1b-45b4-b53f-df3e968b9505/_apis/wit/attachments/305ce5ba-de37-42cc-a681-464e84d9e57c?fileName=image.png\" alt=Image><br> </div><div><br> </div><div><b>Risk/Impact (Mention Testing Impact Areas if any):</b><br> </div><div>Restricted impact to TOPs using this functionality (PL, Task, NC) images.<br> </div><div><br> </div><div><b>Recommended Testing for Certification:</b><br> </div><div><span style=\"display:inline !important;\">Test TOPs using this functionality (PL, Task, NC) images.</span><br> </div><div><br> </div><div><b>Site URL:</b><br> </div><div><a href=\"https://sc-features.intergraph.com/TR-5194599\">https://sc-features.intergraph.com/TR-5194599</a> <br> </div><div><br> </div><div><b>User Story Acceptance Checklist:</b><br> </div><div>Any impact to performance? No<br> </div><div>Any impact to backward compatibility? No<br> </div><div>Any impact on other supported platforms? No<br> </div><div>Any impact to upgrade situations(including schema or model changes)? No<br> </div><div>Any impact to non - English environments? &nbsp;No<br> </div><div>Any impact to error cases / what if situations / negative tests? &nbsp; No<br> </div><div>Any impact to documentation? &nbsp;No<br> </div><div>Any impact to existing regression scripts? &nbsp; No<br> </div><div>Any impact to other areas of the product or downstream products? &nbsp; No<br> </div><div>Has this been covered by ATPs now? Yes<br> </div><span>Has Root Cause Analysis been done? Yes</span><br><div><span><br></span> </div><div><b>ATP:</b> </div><div>ImgtoPDFwTitle_Test (Existing)<br> </div>",
